    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 99.</p><p>Heroic Perk: Shroud of Night</p><p>Prerequisite: Living Shadow, Phantom Strike</p><p>You can cast the Darkness spell innately and at will, requiring no material components. Dexterity is your spellcasting ability for this spell. As a bonus action, you can extend your inner shadow outward in a 60-foot radius, turning the area to magical darkness for 1 minute. Creatures of your choice within this darkness can see through it.</p></div>",
